        In accumulator: ForkJoinPool.commonPool-worker-1
        In combiner: ForkJoinPool.commonPool-worker-1
        In accumulator: ForkJoinPool.commonPool-worker-1
        In combiner: ForkJoinPool.commonPool-worker-1
        In combiner: ForkJoinPool.commonPool-worker-1
        {a=3, b=2, c=1}
        */
    }
